================================================================================
liminal-experiment
================================================================================

KEYBINDINGS
-----------

Esc        - quit
Mouse      - rotational movement
W, A, S, D - translational movement
LClick     - interact
T          - toggle flashlight
Y          - toggle noclip
Q          - cycle mouse grab mode & fullscreen game
LShift     - sprint
LCtrl      - crouch
+          - increase look sense
-          - lower look sense

BUILDING
--------

$ cargo +nightly build --release

The exe will be in ./target/release

RUNNING
-------

Double click the ./backrooms_liminal.exe

Or, run
	$ ./backrooms_liminal.exe -- <seed>

TEXTURE & RESOURCE
------------------

https://github.com/amini-allight/backrooms-textures
https://backrooms-freewriting.fandom.com/wiki/Almond_Water
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/search/backrooms/
